<p class="">Although you were in favour in September?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-51d7c61f-9f4c-4ee1-841d-01d4ec64131e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
